2. Inode numbers of all files
Command: ls -li original_file.txt hard_link.txt sym_link.txt
Output:
46434 -rw-rw-r-- 2 muskan_bhardwaj muskan_bhardwaj 21 Jul  3 17:14 hard_link.txt
46434 -rw-rw-r-- 2 muskan_bhardwaj muskan_bhardwaj 21 Jul  3 17:14 original_file.txt
